	uccessful rock band of the 1980's\, The Police\, composer of film scores\,
	 video games and operas\, multi Grammy winner and Rock and Roll Hall of Fa
	mer\, writer and film maker\, is heading out on his first American spoken-
	word tour\, to talk about it all in his usual funny\, intelligent\, sharp 
	and unique way. An evening of conversation\, with photos\, videos and a Q&
	A. The Neptune is located at 1303 Northeast 45th Street in Seattle's Unive
	rsity District. There is a ticket limit of 8 tickets per person and per cr
